  <brief_title>GlideScope Groove Versus Macintosh Blade for Double-Lumen Endotracheal Tube Intubation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of GlideScope Groove to Macintosh Blade for Orotracheal Intubation With Double-Lumen Endotracheal Tube: a Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Lawson Health Research Institute</agency>
